data.description: This charming 2-story home in a quiet cul-de-sac is now on the market. It welcomes you with its inviting interior, adorned with tile floors and a neutral color palette. The spacious living room is perfect for gatherings, while the eat-in kitchen is equipped with wood cabinets, built-in appliances, and a peninsula with a 2-tier breakfast bar. The home also boasts a sizable loft, versatile for use as an entertainment area or game room. The main bedroom offers comfort and privacy, complete with a private bathroom featuring dual sinks and a walk-in closet. Outside, the sizable backyard is an entertainer's dream, hosting a covered patio, built-in BBQ, Gazebo, an above-ground hot tub, and a shimmering pool. This home is the perfect blend of comfort and convenience, waiting just for you!
